      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 77.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 77.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天之道，損有餘而補不足。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It is the Way of Heaven to diminish superabundance, and to supplement deficiency.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-077__align-005">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
